      "message": "I strongly disagree with presenting this method in official docs. It makes onap user unsecure as consul UI is unprotected and that's main reason why it is not exposed as a nodeport.\n\nI would prefer that we describe only kubectl proxy method to be sure that only people who really know what they are doing would expose consul to the outside world.\n\n@Sylvain\nWhat's your point of view?",
